s every 8 hours at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC, based on the premium between perpetual and spot prices. The funding rate is exchanged between long and short position holders, with MEXC taking no cut from the funding payments. Zero maker fees on MEXC allow traders to enter and exit positions for funding collection without paying trading fees, making it particularly attractive for high-frequency funding rate strategies."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
